A BILL TO BE ENTITLED
AN ACT
1 To amend Chapter 1 of Title 43 of the Official Code of Georgia Annotated, relating to
2 general provisions of professions and businesses, so as to provide for the issuance of digitally
3 verifiable licenses for spouses of military service members, spouses of transitioning service
4 members, and transitioning military service members; to provide definitions; to provide for
5 the adoption of rules and regulations; to provide for the issuance of physical licenses upon
6 request; to provide for related matters; to repeal conflicting laws; and for other purposes.
7 BE IT ENACTED BY THE GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF GEORGIA:
8 SECTION 1.
9 Chapter 1 of Title 43 of the Official Code of Georgia Annotated, relating to general
10 provisions of professions and businesses, is amended by adding a new Code section to read
11 as follows:
12 "43-1-37.
13 (a) As used in this Code section, the term:
14 (1) 'Digitally verifiable license' means a license that:
15 (A) Can be accessed electronically;
16 (B) Has a digital signature;
